BUSINESS RULE SPECIFICATIONS

RULE INFORMATION

Statement:  A carpet that has been loaned to a customer cannot be returned before it was originally loaned out. 

Constraint: ActualCarpetReturnDate must be later than TrialPeriodStartDate

